item.title: Hand crafted Macramé Cord Earrings
item.dc:creator: admin
item.description: Discover the beauty of craftsmanship with these handmade macramé cord earrings, perfect for adding a bohemian touch to your ensemble. Crafted from durable,leftover lightweight cotton cord, creating delicate yet eye-catching designs.Comfortable for all-day wear, these earrings are hypoallergenic, making them ideal for sensitive ears.
